channel.title: Comments on: The Strokes and Jarvis Cocker cover The Cars’ “Just What I Needed” at Reading

item.title: By: Joseph
item.dc:creator: Joseph
item.description: Why do I like Jarvis Cocker so much? I'm supposed to be seething with rage as he stepped onstage with fashion model/child actor, Julian Casablancas, but I ended up liking Julian. I only like a few Pulp songs and I think his solo albums are crap, well, just the second one. If people have irrational hatred towards bands, I have unexplainable love for Jarvis. I'm not even gay. I just really, really like him. I really do. Did I mention that I like him?
item.content:encoded: Why do I like Jarvis Cocker so much? I’m supposed to be seething with rage as he stepped onstage with fashion model/child actor, Julian Casablancas, but I ended up liking Julian. I only like a few Pulp songs and I think his solo albums are crap, well, just the second one. If people have irrational hatred towards bands, I have unexplainable love for Jarvis. I’m not even gay. I just really, really like him. I really do. Did I mention that I like him?
